data.description: Welcome to 6360 Arbor Ave, an elegant home nestled in a tranquil area of Cocoa, situated on 0.27-acres of land. Upgrades include new appliances, fresh interior & exterior paint, new luxury-vinyl flooring, new kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, smart-home fixtures, and so much more! A 200 sq. ft. detached mother-in-law suite is an added bonus and value-add. Exceptionally ideal location, close to all grocery, restaurants, along with many attractions, recreations, and scenic parks nearby. Visit this home today and prepare to fall in love!
